                  </hi>**—<hi rend="italic">They both</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to previous convictions, Smith at Clerkenwell in April</hi>, 1874, <hi rend="italic">and Robinson at this Court in December</hi>, 1870—<hi rend="italic">
